title: Assault on Sudanese City Bore ‘Hallmarks of Genocide,’ U.N. Finds
summary_full: A paramilitary group in Sudan’s civil war “acted with genocidal intent” in a monthslong siege of El Fasher, according to human rights experts.
summary_public: A paramilitary group in Sudan’s civil war “acted with genocidal intent” in a monthslong siege of El Fasher, according to human rights experts.
